myVelibCore.planningPolicyPackage.PlanningPolicy

  • Packages that use PlanningPolicy 
    Package Description
    myVelibCore.planningPolicyPackage  

    • Uses of PlanningPolicy in myVelibCore.planningPolicyPackage

      Classes in myVelibCore.planningPolicyPackage that implement PlanningPolicy 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AvoidPlusStation
      Avoid plus stations planning policy This belong to the Strategy Pattern Planning policy of a planning ride With this policy the destination station cannot be a plus station
      class  FastestPath
      Fastest path planning policy This belong to the Strategy Pattern Planning policy of a planning ride Source and destination stations are chosen so that the total time of the trip, including the walking part of the trip is minimal, assuming that the average walking speed is 4 Km/h while the average bicycle-riding speed is 15 Km/h, for mechanical bikes, and 20 Km/h for electrical bikes.
      class  PreferPlusStation
      Prefer plus stations planning policy This belong to the Strategy Pattern Planning policy of a planning ride With this policy the destination station should be a \plus" station (given a plus station no further away than 10% of the distance of the closest station to the destination location exists).
      class  ShortestPath 
      class  UniformityPolicy
      Uniformity planning policy This belong to the Strategy Pattern Planning policy of a planning ride Preservation of uniformity of bicycles distribution amongst stations: with this policy the choice of the source and destination station is affected by the number of available bikes (at source station) and free slots (at destination).
